[
    {
        "text": "Hello. Welcome to Michael's Better Business English.",
        "startTime": 660,
        "endTime": 3678,
        "slowStartTime": 1140,
        "slowEndTime": 5742
    },
    {
        "text": "This month, we're looking at a very important technique: how to be positive.",
        "startTime": 4284,
        "endTime": 9761,
        "slowStartTime": 6576,
        "slowEndTime": 14866
    },
    {
        "text": "Here, there are two key issues to be careful of.",
        "startTime": 10762,
        "endTime": 13116,
        "slowStartTime": 16293,
        "slowEndTime": 19899
    },
    {
        "text": "First: Attitude.",
        "startTime": 13716,
        "endTime": 15500,
        "slowStartTime": 20724,
        "slowEndTime": 23475
    },
    {
        "text": "Do you have a can't-do attitude or can-do attitude?",
        "startTime": 16243,
        "endTime": 20109,
        "slowStartTime": 24514,
        "slowEndTime": 30389
    },
    {
        "text": "Often, Japanese business people tend to focus on problems,...",
        "startTime": 21274,
        "endTime": 25006,
        "slowStartTime": 32061,
        "slowEndTime": 37734
    },
    {
        "text": "...difficulties or risks in meetings.",
        "startTime": 25083,
        "endTime": 27486,
        "slowStartTime": 37774,
        "slowEndTime": 41454
    },
    {
        "text": "This can have a bit of a negative impression on other people.",
        "startTime": 28048,
        "endTime": 31113,
        "slowStartTime": 42222,
        "slowEndTime": 46894
    },
    {
        "text": "Other cultures such as Western cultures prefer a can-do approach.",
        "startTime": 31935,
        "endTime": 36467,
        "slowStartTime": 48052,
        "slowEndTime": 54926
    },
    {
        "text": "Rather than focusing on problems or risks, what are the solutions or opportunities?",
        "startTime": 36946,
        "endTime": 42892,
        "slowStartTime": 55569,
        "slowEndTime": 64563
    },
    {
        "text": "Secondly, use positive language to be positive and show a can-do attitude.",
        "startTime": 44728,
        "endTime": 50189,
        "slowStartTime": 67242,
        "slowEndTime": 75509
    },
    {
        "text": "Try using not, plus a positive word instead of a negative word.",
        "startTime": 51185,
        "endTime": 56815,
        "slowStartTime": 76928,
        "slowEndTime": 85448
    },
    {
        "text": "For example: \"This quarter, sales were bad.\"",
        "startTime": 57472,
        "endTime": 60969,
        "slowStartTime": 86358,
        "slowEndTime": 91678
    },
    {
        "text": "Better: \"This quarter, sales were not so good.\"",
        "startTime": 61854,
        "endTime": 65824,
        "slowStartTime": 92931,
        "slowEndTime": 98961
    },
    {
        "text": "Still the same basic meaning but a more positive feeling.",
        "startTime": 66559,
        "endTime": 70247,
        "slowStartTime": 99988,
        "slowEndTime": 105595
    },
    {
        "text": "Also, try balancing a negative point with a positive one.",
        "startTime": 72332,
        "endTime": 76329,
        "slowStartTime": 108648,
        "slowEndTime": 114718
    },
    {
        "text": "For example: \"Sales last year were not so good\"...",
        "startTime": 77027,
        "endTime": 80565,
        "slowStartTime": 115690,
        "slowEndTime": 121073
    },
    {
        "text": "...\"but this year, they're looking much better.\"",
        "startTime": 81162,
        "endTime": 83853,
        "slowStartTime": 121893,
        "slowEndTime": 126005
    },
    {
        "text": "And finally, try to use more positive words in your speech.",
        "startTime": 85590,
        "endTime": 89780,
        "slowStartTime": 128535,
        "slowEndTime": 134895
    },
    {
        "text": "Words like successful, excellent, wonderful, great or exciting.",
        "startTime": 90393,
        "endTime": 96777,
        "slowStartTime": 135740,
        "slowEndTime": 145391
    },
    {
        "text": "This will help give a positive impression to the mind of the listener.",
        "startTime": 97499,
        "endTime": 101439,
        "slowStartTime": 146398,
        "slowEndTime": 152384
    },
    {
        "text": "So, use these techniques and you can be positive too.",
        "startTime": 102705,
        "endTime": 106767,
        "slowStartTime": 154208,
        "slowEndTime": 160376
    },
    {
        "text": "Thank you and good luck.",
        "startTime": 107619,
        "endTime": 109061,
        "slowStartTime": 161578,
        "slowEndTime": 163817
    }
]